## #gpio-cells

**Value type:** `<u32>`

The *#gpio-cells* property defines the number of cells required to encode a GPIO specifier for this GPIO controller. Used by GPIO controller nodes to indicate how many `<u32>` cells follow the phandle in GPIO references. A common value is 2 (pin number + flags).

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun50i-h6.dtsi */
pio: pinctrl@300b000 {
    gpio-controller;
    #gpio-cells = <3>;
};
```
